{"tid":2383392,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳業坤赴日Working Holiday兩個月 零工作朝朝10點醒自嘲「待業坤」","createTime":"2021-01-28T01:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T10:09:09.000Z","uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"bf1afc96100122d2ba31adde870baa17f0a8a809","tid":2383392,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:05:38.000Z","msg":"吳業坤「坤哥」去年11月專程飛往日本，趁30歲前進行Working Holiday。但坤哥喺當地日日瞓到黃朝百晏，搵工又抱住「佛系」心態，至今逗留日本兩個幾月都係零工作，仲笑自已目前叫「待業坤」，每朝瞓到呢個時間先醒⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/21_19120223775ffc2fe3c6069.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F01%2F21_19120223775ffc2fe3c6069.jpg&h=1f34e2ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然持Working Holiday Visa（工作假期簽證）到日本，但吳業坤直言仍未搵到工，他笑言：「我帶咗幾萬蚊港幣嚟，應該夠用。」"},{"pid":"55ed3e861bc8030330bf84f9e7152a8328b68f3e","tid":2383392,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:05:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/kwangorrrrrr_123267516_2873936436167646_2675741684713814980_n_3999903336010d62cc141f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F01%2Fkwangorrrrrr_123267516_2873936436167646_2675741684713814980_n_3999903336010d62cc141f.jpg&h=505422e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/kwangorrrrrr_123290560_1717960735029567_9032998151198945088_n_155410516010d629aff5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F01%2Fkwangorrrrrr_123290560_1717960735029567_9032998151198945088_n_155410516010d629aff5a.jpg&h=3965a678&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n空手道班同學年齡介乎5-15歲所以好少交流。"},{"pid":"638651d341f30ddee07514f658c89e6b4cc8896f","tid":2383392,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:06:05.000Z","msg":"坤哥去年11月趁住未超齡，專程飛到日本進行Working Holiday，至今已逗留超過兩個幾月。日前接受鄭裕玲「Do姐」電台節目訪問，自爆兩個月嚟都抱住「佛系」心態搵工，佢話：「其實日日瞓到自然醒，瞓醒都10點後，做運動醒下個人，之後就出去食飯，食飽睇下日文書好快到夜晚，開頭都諗住搵工，但係唔知幾時返香港，所以算啦，變咗no working嘅working holiday！」佢仲笑自已目前叫「待業坤」，坤哥陣毒男味出晒嚟。"},{"pid":"1de73cbd5af3ef53e7da91bf90881618150a6e15","tid":2383392,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:06:24.000Z","msg":"訪問中坤哥話喺日本因為太得閒，毒到匿埋上網學捲脷，學足一星期。之後，Do姐好心提議佢拍下旅行片擺上網同大家分享，點知坤哥不離毒男本色話：「未體驗到啲乜，冇咩衝擊，揸住部相機，好似硬要拍啲嘢出嚟，算啦，真係遇到特別先。」訪問到最後，Do姐終於忍唔住問佢唔悶咩？坤哥先話：「有啲思鄉，原來兩個月唔工作，都有諗覺得自己好似好廢！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/140308227_241420797388075_1471709781349151577_n_677818866600d22aee5602.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F01%2F140308227_241420797388075_1471709781349151577_n_677818866600d22aee5602.jpg&h=65fae581&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8f39131ea53c0b5e04c2557a2df61934e80591c","tid":2383392,"uid":184233,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:06:34.000Z","msg":"坤狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6ee43f4cebcadb662a0e327d5403c30d0c1a4f","tid":2383392,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:06:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/kwangorrrrrr_94977655_1709366875872694_5744055011348679069_n_8351930586010d662d1b73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F01%2Fkwangorrrrrr_94977655_1709366875872694_5744055011348679069_n_8351930586010d662d1b73.jpg&h=7be22581&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n離港兩個幾月，話自己開始思鄉。"},{"pid":"c8b0ff5360f9995169546412e0d49a98e86f8dcb","tid":2383392,"uid":274722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:08:00.000Z","msg":"香港我最喜愛男歌手去日本working holiday.[sos"},{"pid":"379568ece720b469e277a986eabe8730753bad55","tid":2383392,"uid":211461,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:11:58.000Z","msg":"偽毒去日本積極昆架妹 食老軟博入籍 唔通照直講咩"},{"pid":"22b8d4d274af1e58d4e7d8e4b80e0e6d0344212e","tid":2383392,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:12:53.000Z","msg":"唔洗供樓？ 定佢fullpay左"},{"pid":"3d084c9927b6f620d1a11841fb5ef0f8c6d6e83d","tid":2383392,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:14:20.000Z","msg":"去大灣區啦"},{"pid":"05f2774bf67c4e0a3c8e29bb86fe860eacf1e674","tid":2383392,"uid":112316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:25:16.000Z","msg":"呢條垃圾"},{"pid":"32b5d8c236ffaa6e57830887eff7b0ed263d73d4","tid":2383392,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T02:13:44.000Z","msg":"型棍子咗"},{"pid":"db43ca65e0194c984251be5cf416831741557431","tid":2383392,"uid":44489,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22b8d4d274af1e58d4e7d8e4b80e0e6d0344212e","tid":2383392,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:12:53.000Z","msg":"唔洗供樓？ 定佢fullpay左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T02:15:16.000Z","msg":"應該fullpay左 放租 自己住番公屋"},{"pid":"7a034aa7bea4c825ecadaf8c79da8caae649e077","tid":2383392,"uid":334957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T02:15:25.000Z","msg":"偽毒坤去日本食唔少好西<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef38b11244ccc504cea7f25124f958d7db406d4","tid":2383392,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T02:16:49.000Z","msg":"點解唔試下busking，是咪無帶結他過去？咁懶唔得喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"098c65edd2e1d703b677a239014ec806c2de1cb2","tid":2383392,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55ed3e861bc8030330bf84f9e7152a8328b68f3e","tid":2383392,"uid":44730,"like"